A successful execution of [lzCompose(ŌĆ”)](https://github.com/code-423n4/2024-03-canto/blob/1516028017a34ccfb4b0b19f5c5f17f5fa4cad42/contracts/asd/asdRouter.sol#L52-L111) ends with a call to [_sendASD(ŌĆ”)](https://github.com/code-423n4/2024-03-canto/blob/1516028017a34ccfb4b0b19f5c5f17f5fa4cad42/contracts/asd/asdRouter.sol#L130-L167) :

